|accessdate=22 October 2009
}}</ref> but only as correspondent.<ref name=IFTN_200091022>
{{cite news
|url=http://www.iftn.ie/broadcast/?act1=record&only=1&aid=73&rid=4282633&tpl=archnews&force=1
