{{cite news
|url=http://www.insideireland.ie/index.cfm/section/news/ext/seanwhelan001/category/1087
|title=Sean Whelan appointed RT<U+00C9> Economics Correspondent
|date=October 21 2009
|work=Inside Ireland.ie
|accessdate=22 October 2009
}}</ref> When elected, Lee was referred to as a "Celebrity TD".<ref name=KA_20091009>
{{cite news
|url=http://www.advertiser.ie/kilkenny/article/17845
